1. Textual Inputs (Single-line)
Control	HTML
Text Input	<input type="text">
Password	<input type="password">
Email	<input type="email">
Number	<input type="number">
Search	<input type="search">
Telephone	<input type="tel">
URL	<input type="url">
2. Textual Inputs (Multi-line)
Control	HTML
Textarea	<textarea>
3. Choice Inputs (Single/Multiple Selection)
Dropdown / Select
Control	HTML
Select Dropdown	<select>
Option	<option>
Radio Buttons
Control	HTML
Radio	<input type="radio">
Checkboxes
Control	HTML
Checkbox	<input type="checkbox">
Datalist (Autocomplete)
Control	HTML
Datalist	<datalist>
Bound Input	<input list="id">
4. Buttons
Control	HTML
Button	<button>
Submit	<input type="submit">
Reset	<input type="reset">
Basic Button	<input type="button">
5. File & Upload Controls
Control	HTML
File Upload	<input type="file">
6. Date & Time Controls
Control	HTML
Date	<input type="date">
Datetime (local)	<input type="datetime-local">
Month	<input type="month">
Time	<input type="time">
Week	<input type="week">
7. Range & Sliders
Control	HTML
Range Slider	<input type="range">
8. Color Picker
Control	HTML
Color Picker	<input type="color">
9. Hidden & Misc Inputs
Control	HTML
Hidden Field	<input type="hidden">
Image Button	<input type="image">
